_Tetra_ is a simple application that was made to test my [3D engine](https://github.com/pedroth/Learning/tree/master/src/main/java/windowThreeDim), made from scratch[^1]. It lets you see some *triangular meshes*, which includes some random *planets*, as you can see in the videos below.

![Showing some *meshes*](https://youtu.be/EWfagjIxd4g)

![Showing some **planets**](https://youtu.be/SeJcezzg_ow)



Feel free to download the program below.

