## Running with docker

Copy paste to a terminal:

```sh
xhost + && sudo docker run --rm -v /tmp/.X11-unix:/tmp/.X11-unix:ro -e DISPLAY=$DISPLAY -it pedroth/java-apps bash -c "java -cp Learning/learning.jar apps.Tetra"
```

[^1]: Just used standard Java8 without any dependencies or OpenGL
